### Test Sequence: Full Migration Query Flow
# 1. Send task request
POST {{host}}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "jsonrpc": "2.0",
    "method": "message/send",
    "params": {
        "message": {
            "role": "user",
            "parts": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I am a doctor in mauritius wanting to move to USA with $10000"
                }
            ]
        }
