    "id": 1
}

### 2. Get task result (replace task-id with the ID from above response)
POST {{host}}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "jsonrpc": "2.0",
    "method": "tasks/get",
    "params": {
        "id": "task-id-here"
    },
    "id": 2
}

